data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! A lot of clean up has been done and this house is ready for you  to give it your special attention!Welcome to your own private retreat in the heart of Archer, FL. This lovely concrete block country home is nestled on a sprawling 5.45-acre wooded lot, offering tranquility and seclusion while still being conveniently located. The location is unbelievable!   Key Features:  Spacious Three Bedrooms: This home features three generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for your family or guests. The master bedroom is huge, with plenty of room.  Massive brick fireplace - the open floor-plan is enhanced by this beautiful brick fireplace.   Air-conditioning system is a Carrier, and only two years old.   Roof has been repaired, and underlayment added. Only needs shingle or metal.  Two Full Bathrooms: Enjoy the convenience of two full bathrooms, ensuring that everyone has their own space and comfort.  Solid Concrete Block Construction: Built to last, this home boasts a solid concrete block construction, providing durability and energy efficiency.  Two car garage with storage space and laundry room built in the middle.  Country Living: Experience the serene lifestyle of the countryside, with a sense of peace and privacy that only 5.45 acres of wooded land can provide.  Wooded Oasis: The property is enveloped by lush woods, creating a natural sanctuary where you can relax, explore, and connect with nature.  Central Location: Archer, FL is ideally situated in Alachua County, offering the perfect blend of rural living and accessibility to nearby towns and cities. This property is within minutes of Celebration point, and a short drive from 122nd Street. Tucked away on a country road, you will be in the middle of bird-call, deer on your yard, and green woods. Outdoor Opportunities: With over 5 acres at your disposal, you'll have endless opportunities for outdoor activities, gardening, and enjoying the Florida sunshine. Plenty of space to ride a 4 wheeler, if you so desire.  Privacy: Tucked away from the hustle and bustle, this home provides a private and peaceful retreat for you and your family.  Wildlife: Keep an eye out for local wildlife that may frequent the area, adding to the natural beauty of your property.  Ideal for Nature Enthusiasts: Perfect for nature enthusiasts, this property offers opportunities for bird-watching, hiking, and wildlife photography. Don't miss the chance to make this peaceful Archer, FL property your own. Experience the best of country living with the convenience of nearby amenities. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and discover the serenity of this concrete block home on 5.45 acres in Alachua County. Yes, this property NEEDS WORK! This is why we have priced it at this price point. But the floor-plan is OPEN, and no major relocation of electricity or water is needed to take advantage of this amazing floor plan! Property is priced to SELL.
